cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.DS 

This paper proposes a learning-based supervised discrete hashing method for large-scale image retrieval, video, and document searches. Therefore, the most likely category is computer vision (cs.CV), followed by information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG). Multimedia (cs.MM) and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS) are also possible categories since the paper discusses computation time and optimization methods.
